sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant B as BalanceController
    participant R as UserRepository
    participant D as H2 Database

    C->>B: GET /balance?userId={id}
    B->>R: findById(userId)
    R->>D: Query UserRecord
    alt User exists
        D-->>R: UserRecord(balance)
        R-->>B: Optional<UserRecord>
        B-->>C: Balance { amount = user.balance }
    else User missing
        D-->>R: No row
        R-->>B: Optional.empty
        B-->>C: Balance { amount = 0.0 }
    end
